text: Carly Joy Wessels (born 13 October 1994) is a South African water polo player. She competed for the South Africa women's national water polo team in the 2014 FINA Women's Water Polo World Cup, 2017 World Aquatics Championships, and 2018 FINA Women's Water Polo World League. == References == Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:South African water polo players
